					"code" : "History invMtof,cachedModL,cachedModR;\n\nHistory sizeMonoModL(1);\nHistory sizeMonoModR(1);\n\nParam pGrainSize(250);\n\nParam pNotePress,pNoteSlide;\n\nParam pVariationToGrain,\n\tpKeyToSize,pVelToSize,pNotePressToSize,pNoteSlideToSize,\n\tpEnv2ToSize,pLFOToSize;\n\nif (invMtof == 0){\n\tinvMtof = 1/mtof(0);\n}\n\n// --- modulation source signals ---\nLFOL = in1;\nLFOR = in2;\nenv2 = in3;\nvarL = in4;\nvarR = in5;\nrpRelativeKey = in6;\nrpRelativeVelocity = in7;\n\nkeyMod = rpRelativeKey * pKeyToSize;\nvelMod = rpRelativeVelocity * pVelToSize;\nmpeMod =  (pNoteSlideToSize * pNoteSlide + pNotePressToSize * pNotePress) * 24;\nenvMod = env2 * pEnv2ToSize;\nsizeMonoMod  =  velMod + keyMod + mpeMod + envMod;\n\nrandomSource = noise();\nrandomModL = randomSource * varL * pVariationToGrain;\nrandomModR = randomSource * varR * pVariationToGrain;\n\nlfoModL = LFOL * pLFOToSize;\nlfoModR = LFOR * pLFOToSize;\n\nsizeModL = sizeMonoMod + randomModL + lfoModL;\nsizeModR = sizeMonoMod + randomModR + lfoModR;\n\nif (sizeModL != cachedModL || sizeModR != cachedModR){\n\tcachedModL = sizeModL;\n\tcachedModR = sizeModR;\n\tsizeMonoModL = mtof(sizeModL) * invMtof;\n\tsizeMonoModR = mtof(sizeModR) * invMtof;\n    }\n\ngrainSizeL = pGrainSize * sizeMonoModL;\ngrainSizeR = pGrainSize * sizeMonoModR;\n\nout1 = grainSizeL;\nout2 = grainSizeR;\n",
